    "name": "噗哟！动脑子",
    "steam_appid": 3336590,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/701e92d0a96a687718033f0724ac7549.avif?t=1768645756\" width=600 height=280 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >噗呦家族来邀请你一起锻炼脑力了。闯过100+精心设计的关卡，闯出个脑力超群！闯出个虎虎生风！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【多变的关卡，趣味的体验】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏拥有100+个关卡可供挑战，内含类推箱子、多种机关转换、方块消除和同时操作多名角色的特殊机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/18c4b573c1fc19ff5063e2fe4a853f38.poster.avif?t=1768645756\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/18c4b573c1fc19ff5063e2fe4a853f38.webm?t=1768645756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/18c4b573c1fc19ff5063e2fe4a853f38.mp4?t=1768645756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >推动箱子开拓道路、利用方块填补深色空缺、转动各种机关、操作多名角色共同合作通往终点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/a79d91aaa23f080d5bc28b8da4eef65e.poster.avif?t=1768645756\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/a79d91aaa23f080d5bc28b8da4eef65e.webm?t=1768645756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/a79d91aaa23f080d5bc28b8da4eef65e.mp4?t=1768645756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【百变的主题，别致的冒险】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关特定关卡可以获取皮肤和主题，总计5种类型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/473f289f441e21c698c3af9df1671595.poster.avif?t=1768645756\" width=600 height=375 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/473f289f441e21c698c3af9df1671595.webm?t=1768645756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【脑力的冒险，让我们登顶】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关数量最多的玩家可以登上榜单，通关全部关卡完成脑力锻炼，会获得噗呦家族的认可。（当然，只要你有尝试的勇气，噗呦家族同样会赞赏你！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/c4766968130c52d919f432d363c89a9f.poster.avif?t=1768645756\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/c4766968130c52d919f432d363c89a9f.webm?t=1768645756\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3336590/extras/c4766968130c52d919f432d363c89a9f.mp4?t=1768645756\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1、极具特色的游戏玩法，融合推箱子的新颖解谜体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2、超过100个游戏关卡，为您带来数小时的欢乐时光</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3、5种不同的游戏皮肤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4、在排行榜上留下你的名字</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5、复古的像素画风</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>备注：本游戏致敬GAMEBOY掌机益智游戏黄金时代的经典作品《Kwirk》</strong></h2>",
